label: [{"start":25,"end":27,"text":"鸡瘟","labels":["disease"]},{"start":32,"end":36,"text":"亚洲鸡瘟","labels":["disease"]},{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"鸡新城疫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":13,"end":18,"text":"急性败血性","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 鸡新城疫是由病毒引起的一种急性败血性传染病。俗称“鸡瘟”，即所谓亚洲鸡瘟。本病一年四季均可发生，尤以寒冷和气候多变季节多发。

label: [{"start":5,"end":6,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":20,"end":21,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":36,"end":40,"text":"呼吸困难","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":41,"end":47,"text":"神经机能紊乱","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":48,"end":58,"text":"粘膜和浆膜出血和坏死","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":56,"end":58,"text":"坏死","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":53,"end":55,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":48,"end":50,"text":"粘膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":51,"end":53,"text":"浆膜","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 各种日龄的鸡均能感染，20日龄—60日龄鸡最易感，死亡率也高。主要特征是呼吸困难，神经机能紊乱，粘膜和浆膜出血和坏死。

label: [{"start":44,"end":48,"text":"亚洲鸡瘟","labels":["disease"]},{"start":49,"end":52,"text":"伪鸡瘟","labels":["disease"]},{"start":55,"end":57,"text":"急性","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":57,"end":61,"text":"败血症状","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"鸡新城疫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":26,"end":30,"text":"副粘病毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":33,"end":41,"text":"高度接触性传染病","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 鸡新城疫（New Castle disease），由副粘病毒引起的高度接触性传染病。又称亚洲鸡瘟或伪鸡瘟。常呈急性败血症状。

label: [{"start":5,"end":9,"text":"呼吸困难","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":13,"end":17,"text":"神经紊乱","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":26,"end":30,"text":"死亡率高","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"便稀","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":10,"end":11,"text":"便","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":18,"end":25,"text":"黏膜和浆膜出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":23,"end":25,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":18,"end":20,"text":"黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":21,"end":23,"text":"浆膜","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 主要特征是呼吸困难、便稀、神经紊乱、黏膜和浆膜出血。死亡率高，对养鸡业危害严重。
1926年首先发现于印度尼西亚，不久又在英国新城发现，世界各国均有流行记载。有强毒株和弱毒株两类。病毒分为低毒力型（即缓发型）、中等毒力型（即中发型）、强毒力型（即速发型）3型。

label: [{"start":10,"end":19,"text":"嗜内脏型新城疫病毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":20,"end":24,"text":"鸡科动物","labels":["type"]},{"start":31,"end":33,"text":"家鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":37,"end":39,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":40,"end":43,"text":"成年鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 多数高强度毒力株常属嗜内脏型新城疫病毒。鸡科动物都可患罹本病。家鸡最易感，雏鸡比成年鸡易感性更高。

label: [{"start":8,"end":12,"text":"精神萎顿","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":19,"end":22,"text":"昏睡状","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":47,"end":51,"text":"呼吸困难","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":52,"end":59,"text":"喉部发出咯咯声","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":52,"end":54,"text":"喉部","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":60,"end":64,"text":"粪便稀薄","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":60,"end":62,"text":"粪便","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":65,"end":67,"text":"恶臭","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":13,"end":17,"text":"羽毛松乱","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":13,"end":15,"text":"羽毛","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":62,"end":64,"text":"稀薄","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":23,"end":34,"text":"冠和肉髯暗红色或黑紫色","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":27,"end":30,"text":"暗红色","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":31,"end":34,"text":"黑紫色","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":23,"end":24,"text":"冠","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":25,"end":27,"text":"肉髯","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":35,"end":46,"text":"嗉囔内常充满液体及气体","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":35,"end":37,"text":"嗉囔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":15,"end":17,"text":"松乱","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":39,"end":46,"text":"充满液体及气体","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":54,"end":59,"text":"发出咯咯声","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 可达44摄氏度，精神萎顿，羽毛松乱，呈昏睡状。冠和肉髯暗红色或黑紫色。嗉囔内常充满液体及气体，呼吸困难，喉部发出咯咯声；粪便稀薄、恶臭，一般2～5天死亡。

label: [{"start":24,"end":28,"text":"神经症状","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":35,"end":39,"text":"运动失调","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":40,"end":50,"text":"头向后仰或向一边弯曲","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":40,"end":41,"text":"头","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":31,"end":34,"text":"翅麻痹","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":32,"end":34,"text":"麻痹","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":31,"end":32,"text":"翅","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":29,"end":30,"text":"腿","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":41,"end":44,"text":"向后仰","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":45,"end":50,"text":"向一边弯曲","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 亚急性或慢性型症状与急性型相似，唯病情较轻，出现神经症状，腿、翅麻痹，运动失调，头向后仰或向一边弯曲等，病程可达1～2个月，多数最终死亡。

label: [{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"鸡新城疫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":10,"end":14,"text":"亚洲鸡瘟","labels":["disease"]},{"start":17,"end":29,"text":"禽副流感病毒型新城疫病毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":43,"end":44,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":45,"end":47,"text":"火鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":48,"end":50,"text":"野禽","labels":["type"]},{"start":56,"end":63,"text":"高度接触传染性","labels":["disease"]},{"start":64,"end":69,"text":"致死性疾病","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 鸡新城疫(ND)又称亚洲鸡瘟。是由禽副流感病毒型新城疫病毒(NDV)引起的一种主要侵害鸡、火鸡、野禽及观赏鸟类的高度接触传染性、致死性疾病。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"家禽","labels":["type"]},{"start":11,"end":15,"text":"呼吸困难","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":16,"end":18,"text":"下痢","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":21,"end":25,"text":"神经症状","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":35,"end":42,"text":"粘膜和浆膜出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":40,"end":42,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":38,"end":40,"text":"浆膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":35,"end":37,"text":"粘膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":26,"end":28,"text":"成鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":28,"end":34,"text":"严重产蛋下降","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 家禽发病后的主要特征是呼吸困难，下痢，伴有神经症状，成鸡严重产蛋下降，粘膜和浆膜出血，感染率和致死率高。

label: [{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"鸡新城疫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"鸡瘟","labels":["disease"]},{"start":15,"end":21,"text":"鸡新城疫病毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":24,"end":25,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":37,"end":42,"text":"烈性传染病","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 鸡新城疫（ND）俗称鸡瘟，是由鸡新城疫病毒引起的鸡的一种高度接触性、急性、烈性传染病。

label: [{"start":14,"end":18,"text":"呼吸困难","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"下痢","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":22,"end":28,"text":"神经机能紊乱","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":3,"end":6,"text":"败血症","labels":["disease"]},{"start":29,"end":36,"text":"黏膜和浆膜出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":34,"end":36,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":32,"end":34,"text":"浆膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":29,"end":31,"text":"黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 常呈现败血症经过，主要特征是呼吸困难，下痢，神经机能紊乱，黏膜和浆膜出血。

label: [{"start":2,"end":3,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":9,"end":10,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":15,"end":17,"text":"幼鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":18,"end":20,"text":"中鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":30,"end":32,"text":"老鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 各种鸡和各种年龄的鸡都能感染，幼鸡和中鸡更易感染，两年以上的老鸡易感性降低。

label: [{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":12,"end":15,"text":"带毒鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":65,"end":68,"text":"消化道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":69,"end":72,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":79,"end":81,"text":"皮肤","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":82,"end":84,"text":"黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":21,"end":23,"text":"粪便","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":17,"end":20,"text":"分泌物","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 本病的主要传染源是病鸡和带毒鸡，其分泌物，粪便，以及被污染的饲料、饮水，非易感的野禽、外寄生虫、人畜等均可传播病源。传播途径主要是消化道和呼吸道，也可经损伤的皮肤、黏膜侵入体内。一年四季均可发生。

label: [{"start":11,"end":12,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":17,"end":22,"text":"速发型毒株","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 在非免疫区或免疫低下的鸡群，一旦有速发型毒株侵入，可迅速传播,呈毁灭性流行，发病率和死亡率可达90%以上。

label: [{"start":8,"end":9,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":21,"end":25,"text":"鸡新城疫","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 在大中型养鸡场，鸡群有一定免疫力的情况下，鸡新城疫主要是以一种非典型的形式出现，应引起重视。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"珠鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":3,"end":5,"text":"火鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":6,"end":7,"text":"雉","labels":["type"]},{"start":48,"end":51,"text":"结膜炎","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 珠鸡、火鸡、雉、孔雀也能感染。鸭、鹅对本病有抵抗力。哺乳动物对本病有强大抵抗力，但人偶有感染而患结膜炎。

label: [{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"急性型病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":5,"end":9,"text":"体温升高","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":18,"end":22,"text":"精神萎顿","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":33,"end":44,"text":"冠和肉髯暗红色或黑紫色","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":37,"end":40,"text":"暗红色","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":41,"end":44,"text":"黑紫色","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":33,"end":34,"text":"冠","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":35,"end":37,"text":"肉髯","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":23,"end":27,"text":"羽毛松乱","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":25,"end":27,"text":"松乱","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":29,"end":32,"text":"昏睡状","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":23,"end":25,"text":"羽毛","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 急性型病初体温升高，可达44摄氏度，精神萎顿，羽毛松乱，呈昏睡状。冠和肉髯暗红色或黑紫色。

label: [{"start":0,"end":11,"text":"嗉囔内常充满液体及气体","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"嗉囔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":12,"end":16,"text":"呼吸困难","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":17,"end":24,"text":"喉部发出咯咯声","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":17,"end":19,"text":"喉部","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":25,"end":29,"text":"粪便稀薄","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":30,"end":32,"text":"恶臭","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":27,"end":29,"text":"稀薄","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":25,"end":27,"text":"粪便","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":19,"end":24,"text":"发出咯咯声","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":4,"end":11,"text":"充满液体及气体","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 嗉囔内常充满液体及气体，呼吸困难，喉部发出咯咯声；粪便稀薄、恶臭，一般2～5天死亡。

label: [{"start":24,"end":28,"text":"神经症状","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":35,"end":39,"text":"运动失调","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":40,"end":50,"text":"头向后仰或向一边弯曲","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":40,"end":41,"text":"头","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":31,"end":34,"text":"翅麻痹","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":32,"end":34,"text":"麻痹","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":29,"end":30,"text":"腿","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":31,"end":32,"text":"翅","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":41,"end":44,"text":"向后仰","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":45,"end":50,"text":"向一边弯曲","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 亚急性或慢性型症状与急性型相似，唯病情较轻，出现神经症状，腿、翅麻痹，运动失调，头向后仰或向一边弯曲等，病程可达1～2个月，多数最终死亡。

label: [{"start":13,"end":17,"text":"严格消毒","labels":["control"]},{"start":18,"end":20,"text":"隔离","labels":["control"]},{"start":21,"end":25,"text":"用灭活苗","labels":["control"]},{"start":26,"end":32,"text":"活苗疫苗接种","labels":["control"]},{"start":26,"end":30,"text":"活苗疫苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":22,"end":25,"text":"灭活苗","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 尚无有效治疗药物，只能依靠严格消毒、隔离和用灭活苗和活苗疫苗接种预防。

label: [{"start":9,"end":10,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":39,"end":48,"text":"嗜内脏速发型新城疫","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 各种品种、各种日龄鸡，在不同季节均可感染，并且具有较高的发病率和死亡率，尤其是嗜内脏速发型新城疫，发病率和死亡率可达100%。

label: [{"start":14,"end":17,"text":"成年鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":18,"end":25,"text":"产蛋率明显下降","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 即使是死亡率不高的其他类型，成年鸡的产蛋率明显下降。

label: [{"start":3,"end":4,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 本病是鸡的重要传染病之一，严重威胁着养鸡业的发展，给养鸡业带来惨重的经济损失。
潜伏期2～5天，感染后症状出现的早晚，取决于病毒感染的途径、感染的剂量、宿主种类、年龄、免疫状态、环境条件及其合并感染与否。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":5,"end":9,"text":"呼吸困难","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":13,"end":18,"text":"粪便呈绿色","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":19,"end":23,"text":"精神沉郁","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":24,"end":28,"text":"神经症状","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":43,"end":45,"text":"转圈","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":46,"end":50,"text":"前冲运动","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":51,"end":57,"text":"体态失去平衡","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":71,"end":75,"text":"产蛋停止","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":13,"end":15,"text":"粪便","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":60,"end":62,"text":"头部","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":16,"end":18,"text":"绿色","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"腹泻","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":10,"end":11,"text":"腹","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":29,"end":31,"text":"斜颈","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":30,"end":31,"text":"颈","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":32,"end":37,"text":"腿与翅麻痹","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":35,"end":37,"text":"麻痹","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":32,"end":33,"text":"腿","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":34,"end":35,"text":"翅","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":38,"end":42,"text":"肌肉震颤","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":40,"end":42,"text":"震颤","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":38,"end":40,"text":"肌肉","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":63,"end":70,"text":"面部和肉髯肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":68,"end":70,"text":"肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":63,"end":65,"text":"面部","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":66,"end":68,"text":"肉髯","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 病鸡表现为呼吸困难，腹泻，粪便呈绿色，精神沉郁及神经症状(斜颈，腿与翅麻痹，肌肉震颤，转圈或前冲运动，体态失去平衡等),头部、面部和肉髯肿大，产蛋停止。在流行初期，常表现为急性暴发，可不见任何症状而死亡。
肉眼所见的病理变化取决于感染病毒的毒株。

label: [{"start":22,"end":25,"text":"消化道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":27,"end":29,"text":"炎症","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":10,"end":17,"text":"肠道出血性损害","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":12,"end":17,"text":"出血性损害","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"肠道","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 所以，剖检时，有时以肠道出血性损害为主，全部消化道都有炎症；

label: [{"start":2,"end":9,"text":"肌胃角质膜下层","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":10,"end":14,"text":"腺胃乳头","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":15,"end":21,"text":"十二指肠黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":29,"end":32,"text":"出血点","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":33,"end":36,"text":"出血斑","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":37,"end":39,"text":"溃疡","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 有时肌胃角质膜下层及腺胃乳头、十二指肠黏膜上均有大小不等的出血点、出血斑或溃疡；

label: [{"start":3,"end":7,"text":"盲肠基部","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":16,"end":18,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"坏死","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":29,"end":31,"text":"水肿","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":32,"end":34,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":22,"end":28,"text":"卵巢血管充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":26,"end":28,"text":"充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":22,"end":26,"text":"卵巢血管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":10,"end":15,"text":"淋巴结肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":13,"end":15,"text":"肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":10,"end":13,"text":"淋巴结","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 有时在盲肠基部的孤立淋巴结肿大、出血或坏死；卵巢血管充血、水肿和出血；

label: [{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"水肿","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":17,"end":22,"text":"局灶性坏死","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":0,"end":8,"text":"上呼吸道黏膜充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"充血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"上呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 上呼吸道黏膜充血、水肿；肝脏有小的局灶性坏死；

label: [{"start":2,"end":4,"text":"胆囊","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":5,"end":7,"text":"心脏","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":14,"end":18,"text":"脂肪组织","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"出血","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":19,"end":26,"text":"针头大小出血点","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 有时胆囊和心脏伴有出血，全身脂肪组织有针头大小出血点；

label: [{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"回肠","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":12,"end":16,"text":"直肠黏膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":23,"end":31,"text":"非典型性鸡新城疫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":5,"end":7,"text":"盲肠","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":17,"end":22,"text":"出血性炎症","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 有时只见两盲肠间的回肠和直肠黏膜有出血性炎症，非典型性鸡新城疫常有此病变。
